QuestData.Title: Maw of Souls: Into the Maw of Souls
QuestData.Description:
Our scouts report that the vrykul damned are forced to sail aboard the Naglfar, a ship built of death.
Travel to the Maw of Souls and confront Helya, before she collects any more poor, unfortunate souls.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defeat Helya in Maw of Souls.

Objectives.Objective: Defeat Helya in Maw of Souls
